precis:
Authority to execute and issue an Instrument of Full Powers authorizing
the Hon. Michael H. Wilson or Robert J. Rochon, or David R. Cohen to sign
a Convention between the Government of Canada and the Government of the
ARGENTINE REPUBLIC for the AVOIDANCE OF DOUBLE TAXATION AND THE PREVENTION
OF FISCAL EVASION WITH RESPECT TO TAXES ON INCOME AND ON CAPITAL.
